data-triple-N3.o: "Star Trek: Voyager is a science fiction television series set in the Star Trek universe. The show is set on the other side of the Milky Way galaxy, 75,000 light-years from Earth, during the 2370s. It follows the adventures of the Starfleet vessel USS Voyager, which became stranded in the Delta Quadrant while pursuing a renegade Maquis ship. Both ships' crews merge aboard Voyager to make the estimated 75-year journey home."@en
